Invocation Name: complaint listener
des:
Enable "Complaint Listener", and start complaining! 

Did you have a bad day? Feel free to say vocalize your frustrations to Alexa, she will listen to you. I hope it makes you feel better.

Warning: Some responses may be rude.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
